<plot>This film Stems from a train trip from one end of Canada to the other and back again, and the loss of a friend in a drowning accident. 15 days of train travel from Vancouver to Halifax and back again (1200 km in total). This film is one of the meditations resulting from that trip. A "Fallen Flag" is the railroad term given to a discontinued rail line.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?188231</url></doc>
